    <item>
      <title>可可价格创下新高，给巧克力制造商和消费者带来沉重打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/cocoa-soars-to-fresh-record-in-blow-to-world-s-chocolate-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场努力应对新一轮的供应担忧，纽约可可期货价格创下新高，这增加了已经困扰巧克力制造商和消费者的高成本进一步恶化的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/cocoa-soars-to-fresh-record-in-blow-to-world-s-chocolate-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 12:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺和诺德在丹麦投资 12 亿美元建新工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/novo-nordisk-invests-1-2-billion-in-new-factory-in-denmark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ozempic 生产商诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 为满足其重磅药物的需求采取了两大步，在获得以 117 亿美元收购海外三家大型工厂的批准后不久，该公司又承诺斥资 85 亿丹麦克朗（12 亿美元）在丹麦建造一家新工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/novo-nordisk-invests-1-2-billion-in-new-factory-in-denmark</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币创下 2021 年以来最长周涨幅纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/bitcoin-btc-hits-record-after-longest-weekly-winning-run-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对数字资产的支持，以及对即将将持有该代币的 MicroStrategy Inc. 纳入美国关键股票指数的乐观态度，比特币价格创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/bitcoin-btc-hits-record-after-longest-weekly-winning-run-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 23:49:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价下跌，因中国数据疲软削弱需求前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国公布的一系列经济数据加剧了人们对这一最大进口国需求减弱的担忧，油价在上周上涨后下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率决议前美国股市乐观情绪高涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-ahead-of-china-data-dump-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员为本周晚些时候各大央行即将公布的一系列利率决定做准备，美国股指期货不受其他主要市场低迷表现的影响。比特币创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-ahead-of-china-data-dump-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 22:44:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日铁公司对一家美国标志性钢铁制造商的重磅收购计划面临危险，拜登总统有理由在未来几天内取消这笔交易。美国主要枢纽的原油库存正在下降。严重的牛肉短缺正在损害美国牛肉行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析人士称，萨赫勒军政府不太可能逆转退出贸易集团的进程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/west-african-juntas-given-six-months-to-rethink-trade-bloc-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西非领导人给予马里、尼日尔和布基纳法索六个月的时间重新考虑退出该地区经济集团，作为避免该集团分裂的最后一次努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/west-african-juntas-given-six-months-to-rethink-trade-bloc-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 19:09:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
